  "texts": [
    "The contributions of LLMs to these tasks could be reviewed by a clinician.",
    "However, the notion of allowing LLMs to function without supervision in clinical practice raises ethical concerns.",
    "They have a propensity to produce false information and propagate data bias, which could lead to incorrect medical decisions.",
    "Furthermore, LLMs lack human empathy, which could be a source of mistrust with patients.",
    "Instead, patients are more likely to trust medical advice from a clinician because of the human connection."
